## specimen fields and types

√Imageable
√name - required
√Plant - Belongs_to, required
√Variety - Belongs_to
acquisition_event - has_one
planting_event - has_one
life_cycle_events - has many
√terminated - boolean default false
evaluation - has_one




## location fields and types
√Imageable
√Name - String, required
√LatLong - point
√size in hectares - Float
√soil_quality - Enum (poor, fair, good)
√slope - integer
√altitude - integer
√average_rainfall - integer
√average_temperature - integer
√irrigated - boolean
√notes - text





# inputs
Name
  compost, irrigation, fertilizer, pesticide, mulch

# acquisition event

imageable
specimen belongs_to
date - Date, required
Accession_Number - String
recieved_in_good_condition - bool, required
acquisition_notes - text

# planting event
specimen belongs_to
imageable
location - has_one
date - Date, 
soil preparation - Enum (no-till, planting-station, full-till)
inputs - relation
notes - text

# life_cycle_events
belongs_to specimen
date
event_type
event_id


# harvest event
imageable
date
harvest_quantity
harvest_quantity_unit
harvest_quality integer between 1 and 10
notes - text

# evaluation
date
success - boolean
recommended - boolean
saved_seed - boolean
will_share_seed - boolean
will_plant_again - boolen
notes
